WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:17.578 --> 00:00:22.769
I feel like I'm making a big difference.  I'm learning that 
 the world is a lot bigger than I thought it was.

00:00:25.960 --> 00:00:35.759
You can actually interact with them and learn about their culture.  When you think 
 about Africa, in the United States, you'd never imagine it would be like this.

00:00:38.127 --> 00:00:51.943
I feel really welcome, wherever you go, people always say "you are welcome" - several times.  And on the 
 streets, people wave at you.  The little kids hold your hands, and they just seem very accepting.

00:00:53.661 --> 00:01:07.013
I thought visiting the slave fort was pretty interesting because its one of the places where history is so tangible.  We've always heard 
 about slavery in the classroom, it's a very emotional experience to be here because we get to see it first hand. 

